collection of web pages is called website 

colletion of information is called web pages

browser is a client site and server is a server site 

server:- server provide a domain like url and hosting store whole website code
  front end :- jaha per user interact hota h 

  html:- html language only use for layout and structure

  tags:- tags are reserve keywords 
  types of tags :- 

  container   -> <tagname>content</tagname>
  non container -> <tagname> isme closing tag nahi hota h

  list:- when our data is sequential is called list 
  there are two type of list
  1. orderd list 
  2.unorderd list 

  atributes:- additional property of tags is called attributes
  list attributes= type 

  block element:- 100% width occupy karta h jisse humara content ek ke niche ek show krta h
  inline element:- image or word ke according hight or width occupy krta h
  img tag attributes= src, hight, width, alt 


